      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "20",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "9": {
          "id": "9",
          "speaker": "Isobel",
          "text": "Even after all she's been through, she thinks herself unstoppable - invincible.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "20",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "6": {
              "id": "6",
              "speaker": "Isobel",
              "text": "It all feels like recklessness to me.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "20",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "14": {
                  "id": "14",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Lorroakan can't harm her. Have faith.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "20",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "27": {
                      "id": "27",
                      "speaker": "Isobel",
                      "text": "He can harm her. Just as Ketheric did. She'll survive it, but she can suffer like any of us - and for longer.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "20",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                },
                "7": {
                  "id": "7",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "She's reckless but powerful. Lorroakan is probably already dead.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "20",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "10": {
                      "id": "10",
                      "speaker": "Isobel",
                      "text": "I hope you're right. He sounds like a vile, vile man. I'd have liked to get a few licks in myself, honestly.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "20": {
                          "id": "20",
                          "speaker": "Isobel",
                          "text": "I wanted to help her, but she said she fights better when she knows I'm safe. I understand, I suppose - I feel the same about her.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "4": {
                              "id": "4",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "I'm going to help her in the fight against Lorroakan.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [
                                "Karlach 1",
                                "Wyll 1",
                                "Gale 1",
                                "Shadowheart 1",
                                "Lae'zel 1",
                                "Jaheira 1",
                                "Halsin 1",
                                "Minsc 1"
                              ],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "16": {
                                  "id": "16",
                                  "speaker": "Isobel",
                                  "text": "I'll rest a little easier if you do. You fought well against my father. I imagine a rat like Lorroakan will be nothing in comparison.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": true,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "19": {
                              "id": "19",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "She can take care of herself. She's Dame Aylin, remember?",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "26": {
                                  "id": "26",
                                  "speaker": "Isobel",
                                  "text": "She certainly is. And she always will be, won't she? Gods, I miss her already.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": true,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "17": {
                              "id": "17",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Leave.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": true,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {}
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                "0": {
                  "id": "0",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "You're right. Her temper will get the better of her.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "20",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "29": {
                      "id": "29",
                      "speaker": "Isobel",
                      "text": "That's my greatest fear.",
                      "context": "",
